SEOBlock-module_seo-block__3EG_s" aria-label="block-content"><span class="SEOBlock-module_block-title__2Y9Bq">#ConTenisyPunto</span><div class="SEOBlock-module_block-content__2Aggm"><p>Sabemos que lo //FIX PARA CAMBIAR LINK DE FOOTER EN INTERNA 3 DE AGOSTO DE 2018

  var linkWebtracking = document.querySelector('.fb-footer-content__links > li:nth-child(2) > a');
  if(linkWebtracking){
    linkWebtracking.innerText = 'Seguimiento de mi orden';
    linkWebtracking.setAttribute('href', 'https://www.falabella.com.co/falabella-co/mi-cuenta/buscar-orden');
  }


//Force the expiration of the Fonocompras cookies when coming from /agent/ url
if(_satellite.getVar('page_previousUrl').match(/\/agent\//)){
  document.cookie = "fonoDeliveryFirstTime=false;domain=falabella.com.co;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;path=/falabella-co/;";
  document.cookie = "fonoPagoFirstTime=false;domain=falabella.com.co;expires=Thu, 01 Jan 1970 00:00:01 GMT;path=/falabella-co/;";

//orderby storage setting
var orderByDropdown = document.querySelector('.fb-filters-sort__dropdown .fb-inline-dropdown__link__title');

  if(orderByDropdown){
    function setOrderByChoiceSessionStorage(value){
    	sessionStorage.setItem('orderByValue', value);
  	}
    
  document.addEventListener('input', function(event){
    var selectedOption = document.querySelector('.fb-filters-sort__dropdown option[value="'+event.target.value+'"]');
    if(selectedOption){
      setOrderByChoiceSessionStorage(selectedOption.innerText);
    }
  });

  document.addEventListener('click', function(event){
    if(event.target.className === 'fb-inline-dropdown__list-item__link'){
      var links = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('.fb-filters-sort__dropdown .fb-inline-dropdown__list-item__link'));
      links.forEach(function(presentLink){
        if(presentLink.innerText === event.target.innerText){
          setOrderByChoiceSessionStorage(event.target.innerText);
        }
      })
      
    }
  });
}

//change footers Inversionitas links

var linkInversionitas = document.querySelectorAll('.fb-footer-content__links > li:nth-child(4) > a')[1];
if (linkInversionitas) {
    if (linkInversionitas.innerText === "Inversionistas") {
        linkInversionitas.setAttribute('href', 'https://investors.falabella.com/');
    }
}

// Agent Local Storage/ Vendor Info
var fonocomprasSection = document.querySelector("#containerHeaderMain");
  if (fonocomprasSection) {
        var vendorSection = fonocomprasSection.querySelectorAll("div")[0].innerText.match(/\d+/)[0] || "";
        var tiendaSection = fonocomprasSection.querySelectorAll("div")[4].innerText.match(/Tienda: \((.+)\)/)[1] || "";
        var vendorInfo=tiendaSection + "|" + vendorSection;
	sessionStorage.setItem("vendorInfo",vendorInfo);
}

//add isPLP desktop and mobile

function addIsPLP() {
    //add isPLP desktop and mobile -
    var linksMenu = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLiBold"]');
    linksMenu.forEach(function (el, index) {
        el.href = el.href + '?isPLP=1';
    });
}
function addIsPLPexplorer() {
    var a = document.querySelectorAll('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLiBold"]');
    for (i = 0; i < a.length; i++) {
        a[i].href = a[i].href + '?isPLP=1';
    }

}
function isIE() {
    ua = navigator.userAgent;
    /* MSIE used to detect old browsers and Trident used to newer ones*/
    var is_ie = ua.indexOf("MSIE ") > -1 || ua.indexOf("Trident/") > -1;
    return is_ie;
}
function executeIsPLP() {
    /* Create an alert to show if the browser is IE or not */
    if (isIE()) {
        setTimeout(addIsPLPexplorer, 1000);
    } else {
        addIsPLP();
    }
}
executeIsPLP();

</style><script>_satellite["_runScript8"](function(event, target, Promise) {
function addMarkup() {
    var iframe = document.createElement('iframe');
    iframe.setAttribute('marginwidth', 0);
    iframe.setAttribute('marginheight', 0);
    iframe.setAttribute('scrolling', 'no');
    iframe.setAttribute('frameborder', 0);
    iframe.setAttribute('class', 'chat-widget-panel');

    var aside = document.createElement('aside');
    aside.appendChild(iframe);
    aside.setAttribute('id', 'chat-widget');
    aside.setAttribute('class', 'chat-widget');
    document.body.appendChild(aside);
}

//Add Message listener to hide the chatbot iframe

function handleAmandaClick(amandaState) {
    var src = document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').getAttribute('src');
    if (!src && window.amandaloading !== 'loading') {
        window.amandaloading = 'loading';
        if (_satellite.getVar('isInternalNetwork')) {
            document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').setAttribute('src', 'https://as-ia-colombia-prd-web.azurewebsites.net');
        } else {
            //https://as-ia-colombia-stg-web.azurewebsites.net/chat.html
            //https://as-ia-colombia-prd-web.azurewebsites.net
            document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').setAttribute('src', 'https://as-ia-colombia-prd-web.azurewebsites.net');

        }

        document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').addEventListener('load', function() {
            document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').style.display = "block";
            document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').setAttribute('style', 'position:static;');
            document.querySelector('aside#chat-widget').setAttribute('style', 'z-index:1900;');
            if (document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container')) {
                document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container').style.display = 'none';
            }
          if(window.innerWidth<1023){
          document.querySelector('.chat-widget').style.height="100%"
          document.querySelector('.chat-widget').style.width="100%"
          }
            //postMessage to amanda

            this.contentWindow.postMessage({
                cookie: _satellite.readCookie('JSESSIONID')
            }, '*');
       
          var _this = this;
          var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
          xhr.open('GET', 'https://www.falabella.com.co/rest/model/atg/userprofiling/ProfileActor/fetchSessionInfo');
          xhr.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
          xhr.onload = function() {
              if (xhr.status === 200) {
                  profileSuccessInfoCall(JSON.parse(xhr.responseText), _this);
              }
          };
          xhr.send();
          window.amandaloading = 'loaded';
        })
    } else if (window.amandaloading === 'loaded') {
        document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').style.display = "block";
      
        document.querySelector('aside#chat-widget').setAttribute('style', 'z-index:1900;')
        if (document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container')) {
            document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container').style.display = 'none';
        }
         if(window.innerWidth<1023){
          document.querySelector('.chat-widget').style.height="100%"
          document.querySelector('.chat-widget').style.width="100%"
          }
    }
}

function profileSuccessInfoCall(session, amanda) {
    var xhr = new XMLHttpRequest();
    xhr.open('GET', 'https://www.falabella.com.co/rest/model/atg/userprofiling/ProfileActor/profile-success');
    xhr.setRequestHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
    xhr.onload = function() {
        if (xhr.status === 200) {
           amanda.contentWindow.postMessage({
                    session_info: session /*,
                        profile_success: data*/
                }, '*');
        }
    };
    xhr.send();
}

//Desktop code

function insertAmandaDesktop() {
    window.addEventListener('message', function(e) {
        if (e.data && e.data.amanda === 'close') {
            document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').style.display = "none";
            window.amandaState = handleAmandaClick(window.amandaState);
        }
    });
    //Use the selectors for the new icon that comes with the page
    if (document.querySelector('.fb-masthead-chatbot.fb-masthead-item--chatbot')) {
        document.querySelector('.fb-masthead-chatbot.fb-masthead-item--chatbot').addEventListener('click', function() {
            window.amandaState = handleAmandaClick(window.amandaState);
        });
    }

    window.addEventListener('message', function(e) {
        if (e.data && e.data.amanda === 'close') {
            if (document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container')) {
                document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container').style.display = '';
                document.querySelector('.chat-widget-panel').style.display = "none";
            }
        }
    });
}

function insertAmandaMobile(condition) {
    if (condition && document.querySelector('#item-necesitasayuda')) {

        document.querySelector('#item-necesitasayuda').addEventListener('click', function() {
            document.body.className += ' shadow-inactive';
            window.amandaState = handleAmandaClick(window.amandaState);
            if (document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container')) {
                document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container').style.display = 'none';
            }
            document.querySelector('#header').click();
        });
        window.addEventListener('message', function(e) {
            if (e.data && e.data.amanda === 'close') {
                document.querySelector('aside#chat-widget').removeAttribute('style');
                document.body.className = document.body.className.replace(/\s?shadow-inactive/, '');
            }
        });

    } else {
        var mobileChatbotElement = document.querySelector('#item-necesitasayuda');
        if (mobileChatbotElement) {
            mobileChatbotElement.parentNode.removeChild(mobileChatbotElement);
        }
    }

}

function insertAmandaBubble() {
    var amandaBubbleContainer = document.createElement('div');
    amandaBubbleContainer.setAttribute('id', 'amanda-bubble-container');
    amandaBubbleContainer.className = 'chat-widget-button';

    amandaBubbleContainer.addEventListener('click', function() {
        window.amandaState = handleAmandaClick(window.amandaState);
    });

    document.querySelector('aside#chat-widget').appendChild(amandaBubbleContainer);

    window.addEventListener('message', function(e) {
        if (e.data && e.data.amanda === 'close') {
            if (document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container')) {
                document.querySelector('#amanda-bubble-container').style.display = '';
            }
            if(window.innerWidth<1023){
          document.querySelector('.chat-widget').style.height="";
          document.querySelector('.chat-widget').style.width="";
          }
        }
    });

}

if (typeof window.insertAmandaDesktop !== 'undefined') {
    addMarkup();
    if (window.digitalData && digitalData.page && digitalData.page.pageName === 'home' || document.URL.replace(/\?.*/, '') === "https://www.falabella.com.co/falabella-co/") {
        window.digitalData.page = {
            pageName: "home"
        }
        insertAmandaBubble();
    }
    insertAmandaMobile(true);
    insertAmandaDesktop();
} else {
    window.addAmandaMarkup = addMarkup;
    window.insertAmandaBubble = insertAmandaBubble;
    window.insertAmandaMobile = insertAmandaMobile;
    window.insertAmandaDesktop = insertAmandaDesktop;
}

var api = {
    getAccengageCurrentDate: function(x){
        var hours = x.toString().match(/\d\d:\d\d:\d\d/);
        var day = x.getDate();
        var month = x.getMonth() + 1;
        var year = x.getFullYear();
        var string = year + '-' + month + '-' + day + ' ' + hours;
        return string;    
    }
}
function isSLP(){
    if(digitalData.page.catalyst){
      return true;   
    }
  return false;
}
function accPdpWindowLoads(){
    if (/product/.test(window.location.href)) {
        if(isSLP()){
            if (!window.ACC) return;
            var prices = _satellite.getVar('recs_prices');
            var sku = _satellite.getVar('recs_productSku');
            var imageURL = document.querySelector('[id*="testId-pod-image"]') && document.querySelector('[id*="testId-pod-image"]').getAttribute('src');
            var productName;
            if (document.querySelector('.product-name')) {
                productName = document.querySelector('.product-name').textContent;
            } else {
                productName = undefined;
            }
            var PDPoptions = {
                'view_last_product_sku': sku,
                'view_last_product_time': api.getAccengageCurrentDate(new Date()),
                'view_last_product_url': window.location.href.split('?')[0].split('/N-')[0],
                'view_last_product_price': prices.INTERNET || prices.NORMAL,
                'view_last_product_name': productName,
                'view_last_product_urlimage': imageURL,
                'view_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'), 
                'view_last_product_category_name': _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat1')
            };
            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", PDPoptions]);
        }else{
            if (!window.ACC) return;
            var prices = _satellite.getVar('recs_prices');
            var sku = _satellite.getVar('recs_productSku');
            var imageURL = document.querySelector('.js-pp-gallery-link img') && document.querySelector('.js-pp-gallery-link img').getAttribute('src');
            var productName;
            if (document.querySelector('.fb-product-cta__title')) {
                productName = document.querySelector('.fb-product-cta__title').textContent;
            } else {
                productName = undefined;
            }
            var PDPoptions = {
                'view_last_product_sku': sku,
                'view_last_product_time': api.getAccengageCurrentDate(new Date()),
                'view_last_product_url': window.location.href.split('?')[0].split('/N-')[0],
                'view_last_product_price': prices.INTERNET || prices.NORMAL,
                'view_last_product_name': productName,
                'view_last_product_urlimage': imageURL,
                'view_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'),
                'view_last_product_category_name':digitalData.ecom && digitalData.ecom.cat1?digitalData.ecom.cat1:'' 
            };

            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", PDPoptions]);
        }
    }
}

    XMLHttpRequest.prototype.open = function (method, callurl, async, user, pass) {
        this.addEventListener("readystatechange", function () {
            if(/(addItemToBasket)/.test(this.responseURL)){
                if (this.readyState === 4) {
                    if(isSLP()){
                        var theResponse = JSON.parse(this.response);
                        if (theResponse.success === true) {
                            if (!window.ACC) return;
                            var cat1 = _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat1');
                            var cat2 = _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat2') === null || _satellite.getVar('ecom_cat2') === undefined ? '' : " | ".concat(_satellite.getVar('ecom_cat2'));

                            //BASKET
                            var addToBasketOptions = {
                                'basket_last_product_name': theResponse.state.products[0].name,
                                'basket_last_product_urlimage': theResponse.state.products[0].image.file.replace('http','https'),
                                'basket_last_product_sku': theResponse.state.products[0].skuId,
                                'basket_last_product_url': 'https://www.falabella.com' + theResponse.state.products[0].url,
                                'basket_last_add_cart_time': api.getAccengageCurrentDate(new Date()),
                                'basket_last_product_price': theResponse.state.products[0].price.slice(-1)[0].purchasedPrice,
                                'basket_last_product_category': categories,
                                // 'basket_last_product_category_id': digitalData.ecom.backend === null || digitalData.ecom.backend === undefined ? '' : digitalData.ecom.backend,
                                'basket_last_product_category_id': _satellite.getVar('ecom_backend'),
                                'basket_last_product_category_name':cat1

                            };
                            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", addToBasketOptions]);
                        }
                    }else{
                        var theResponse = JSON.parse(this.response);
                        if (theResponse.success === true) {
                            if (!window.ACC) return;
                            var getDigitalDataEcom = digitalData.ecom;
                            var cat1 = getDigitalDataEcom.cat1;
                            var cat2 = getDigitalDataEcom.cat2 === null || getDigitalDataEcom.cat2 === undefined ? '' : " | ".concat(getDigitalDataEcom.cat2);

                            //BASKET

                                'basket_last_product_name': theResponse.state.products[0].name,

                                'basket_last_product_sku': theResponse.state.products[0].skuId,

                            };
                            ACC.push(["core:updateDeviceInfo", addToBasketOptions]);
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }, false);

var _createClass = (function() {
  function defineProperties(target, props) {
    for (var i = 0; i < props.length; i++) {
      var descriptor = props[i];
      descriptor.enumerable = descriptor.enumerable || false;
      descriptor.configurable = true;
      if ("value" in descriptor) descriptor.writable = true;
      Object.defineProperty(target, descriptor.key, descriptor);
    }
  }
  return function(Constructor, protoProps, staticProps) {
    if (protoProps) defineProperties(Constructor.prototype, protoProps);
    if (staticProps) defineProperties(Constructor, staticProps);
    return Constructor;
  };
})();

function _classCallCheck(instance, Constructor) {
  if (!(instance instanceof Constructor)) {
    throw new TypeError("Cannot call a class as a function");
  }
}

//define methods for interact with ui

var UI = (function() {
  function UI() {
    _classCallCheck(this, UI);
  }

  _createClass(UI, [
    {
      key: "findStyleTag",
      value: function findStyleTag(where, what) {
        var a = document.getElementsByTagName(where)[0].children;
        a = Array.from(a);
        var styleTags = a.filter(function(el) {
          return el.localName === what;
        });
        return styleTags[0];
      }
    },
    {
      key: "createTag",
      value: function createTag(name, content) {
        //return `<meta name="${name}" content="${content}">`
        var meta = document.createElement("meta");
        meta.name = name;
        meta.content = content;
        return meta;
      }
    }
  ]);

  return UI;
})();

//init function

function addMetas() {
  var ui = new UI();
  var firstStyle = ui.findStyleTag("head", "style");

  metaInfo.map(function(el) {
    var tags = ui.createTag(el.name, el.content);
    firstStyle.insertAdjacentElement("beforebegin", tags);
  });
}
addMetas();

function valid(name) {
  // TODO: validate against options dictionary
  return name.indexOf('smartbanner:') !== -1 && name.split(':')[1].length > 0;
}

function convertToCamelCase(name) {
  var parts = name.split('-');
  parts.map(function (part, index) {
    if (index > 0) {
      parts[index] = part.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + part.substring(1);
    }
  });
  return parts.join('');
}

var OptionParser = function () {
  function OptionParser() {
    _classCallCheck(this, OptionParser);
  }

  _createClass(OptionParser, [{
    key: 'parse',
    value: function parse() {
      var metas = document.getElementsByTagName('meta');
      var options = {};
      var optionName = null;
      Array.from(metas).forEach(function (meta) {
        var name = meta.getAttribute('name');
        var content = meta.getAttribute('content');
        if (name && content && valid(name) && content.length > 0) {
          optionName = name.split(':')[1];
          if (Array.from(optionName).includes('-')) {
            optionName = convertToCamelCase(optionName);
          }
          options[optionName] = content;
        }
      });
      return options;
    }
  }]);

  return OptionParser;
}();

exports.default = OptionParser;

    setContentPosition(event.data.height);
  }

  }
}

            }

        }

        if (!windowW && type === "row") {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                if (menuLink.closest('.secondLevelMenu__title')) {
                    return 0;
                } else {
                    var thirdLevelContainer = menuLink.closest('.thirdLevelMenu');
                    var thirdLevelLinkArr = [].slice.apply(thirdLevelContainer.querySelectorAll('li'));
                    var clickedThirdLevel = menuLink.closest('li');
                    return thirdLevelLinkArr.indexOf(clickedThirdLevel) + 1;

                }

            } else {
                if (menuLink.closest('[class*=SecondLevelItems_submenuTitleCon]')) {
                    return 0;
                } else {
                    var clickedThirdLevel = menuLink.closest('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_listElements"]');
                    var thirdLevelLinkArr = [].slice.apply(menuLink.closest('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_leafNodes"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="ThirdLevelItems_listElements"]'));
                    return thirdLevelLinkArr.indexOf(clickedThirdLevel) + 1;
                }
                return;
            }

        }
        var filterColum = function() {
            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                if (windowW) {
                    var a = columnOrder.find(function(el) {
                        if (el.querySelector('.secondLevelMenu__title--active')) {
                            return el.querySelector('.secondLevelMenu__title--active');
                        }
                    });
                    return [].slice.apply(a.querySelectorAll('.secondLevelMenu__mobile'));
                } else {
                    return columnOrder;
                }
            } else {
                return columnOrder;
            }
        };
        filterColum().map(function(el, i) {
            var rgx = el.textContent;

            var title = function() {
                if (ui.isSLP()) {
                    return el.innerText.split("\n", 1)[0];
                } else {
                    return el.textContent.substr(0, secondLevelDescription.length);
                }
            };

            var theParent = function() {
                if (windowW) {
                    return linkTo;
                } else {
                    if (menuLink.className.indexOf("thirdLevelMenu--link") > -1 || menuLink.className.indexOf("ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLi") > -1) {
                        return ui.isSLP() ? menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement : menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement
                    } else {
                        return menuLink.parentElement.parentElement;
                    }
                }
            };
            var secondLevelDescription = ui.secondLevelDescription(theParent());

            if (title() === secondLevelDescription) {

                if (rgx.indexOf(menuLink.textContent.trim()) > -1) {
                    var indexColumn = i;
                    var thisSlpTitle = ui.isSLP() ? /__title/.test(menuLink.className) : /_submenuTitle/.test(menuLink.className);
                    if (thisSlpTitle) {
                        if (menuLink.textContent === el.querySelector('[class*="_submenuTitle"]').textContent) {
                            switch (type) {
                            case "column":
                                order = indexColumn;
                                break;
                            case "row":
                                order = /\<\/a>/.test(menuLink.outerHTML) ? indexColumn = 0 : indexColumn + 1;
                                break;
                            default:
                                console.log("not column or row");
                                break;
                            }
                        }
                    } else {
                        var isSLPListElement = ui.isSLP() ? el.querySelectorAll('li') : el.querySelectorAll("[class*=ThirdLevelItems_listElements]");
                        // var thirdLink = windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__mobile"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=thirdLevelMenu') : isSLPListElement;
                        var thirdLink = function() {
                            if (ui.isSLP()) {
                                return windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="secondLevelMenu__mobile"] .secondLevelMenu__content').querySelectorAll('[class*=thirdLevelMenu') : isSLPListElement;
                            } else {
                                // return windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="SecondLevelItems_displaySubMenuMobile"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=ThirdLevelItems_activeMobileThirdLevel] li') : isSLPListElement;
                                return windowW ? menuLink.closest('[class*="activeMobileThirdLevel"]').querySelectorAll('[class*=ThirdLevelItems]') : isSLPListElement;
                            }
                        };
                        thirdLink = [].slice.apply(thirdLink());
                        thirdLink.map(function(el, i) {
                            if (el.textContent.trim() === menuLink.textContent.trim()) {
                                switch (type) {
                                case "column":
                                    order = indexColumn;
                                    break;
                                case "row":
                                    order = ui.isSLP() ? i - 1 : i + 1;
                                    break;
                                default:
                                    console.log("not column or row");
                                    break;
                                }
                            }
                        });
                    }
                }
            }
        });
        return order;
    }
};

function execute() {
    var windowW = window.screen.width < 1024;
    var topLevelMenu = document.querySelector('.hamburgerBtn') ? document.querySelectorAll('.hamburgerBtn') : document.querySelectorAll('.fb-masthead__new-hamburger-menu [class*="_firstCategories"],[class*="CategoryMenuButton-module_menu-toggle-button"]');
    var validateServer = digitalData.page.serverName;
    if (topLevelMenu.length === 0)
        return;
    document.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
        var menuLink = windowW ? event.target : event.target.closest('a');
        if (menuLink && ui.approvedTrackClick(menuLink)) {
            var firstLevelPosition = ui.firstLevelPosition() + 1;
            var firstLevelDescription = ui.firstLevelDescription();
            var linkTo = event.target || event.target.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.querySelector('[class*="submenuTitleToggleActive"]');
            var theParent = function() {
                if (windowW) {
                    return linkTo;
                } else {
                    if (menuLink.className.indexOf("thirdLevelMenu--link") > -1 || menuLink.className.indexOf("ThirdLevelItems_submenuElementLi") > -1) {
                        return ui.isSLP() ? menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement : menuLink.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement
                    } else {
                        return menuLink.parentElement.parentElement;
                    }
                }
            };
            var secondLevelDescription = ui.secondLevelDescription(theParent());
            var thirdLevelDescription = menuLink.textContent.trim() !== "" && menuLink.textContent.trim() !== "arrow" ? menuLink.textContent.trim() : secondLevelDescription;

            var columnOrder = ui.order(menuLink, 'column');
            var rowOrder = ui.order(menuLink, 'row') === -1 ? 0 : ui.order(menuLink, 'row');

            if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));
                sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));

            }

            sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', firstLevelDescription + '|' + secondLevelDescription + '|' + thirdLevelDescription + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + columnOrder + '|' + rowOrder);

        }
        if (/img_banner/.test(event.target.className)) {
            var firstLevelPosition = ui.firstLevelPosition();
            var topCategory = event.target.parentElement.parentElement.parentElement.closest('[class*="submenuStage"]').querySelector('[class*="FirstLevelItems_menuElementsHover"]').textContent;
            var ImgName = event.target.src.match(/([^\/]+)\?|([^\/]+)\.gif|([^\/]+)\.jpg|([^\/]+)\.jpeg/)[0].replace('?', '');
            if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str(topCategory, 'B1', ImgName, firstLevelPosition, '50', '1'));
            }
            sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', topCategory + '|' + 'B1' + '|' + ImgName + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + '50' + '|' + '1');
        }
        if (event.target.closest('[class*="CategoryMenuDesktop-module_category-content-container"],[class*="CategoryMenuMobile-module_mobile-menu-container"]')) {
            if (window.screen.width < 1024) {
                //dosomething
                if (event.target.closest('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-2"]') || event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category"]') && event.target.localName !== "svg" && !/CategoryMenuButton-module_hamburger/i.test(event.target.className)) {
                    var columnCollection = [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('[data-testid="first-level-category"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-2"]'));
                    var linksCollection = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]') ? [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]').querySelectorAll('[class*="MenuBody-module_leaf-category-item"]')) : [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-2"]').parentElement.parentElement.querySelectorAll('[class*="MenuBody-module_leaf-category-item"]'));
                    var firstLevelCollection = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('[class*="AccordionContent-module_level-button-1"]'));

                    var firstLevelPosition = firstLevelCollection.indexOf(document.querySelector('[class*=AccordionContent-module_level-button-1][class*=AccordionContent-module_active]'))+1;
                    var firstLevelDescription = document.querySelector('[class*=AccordionContent-module_level-button-1][class*=AccordionContent-module_active]').innerText;
                    var columnOrder = columnCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('[data-testid="first-level-category"]').querySelector('[class*=AccordionContent-module_level-button-2][class*=AccordionContent-module_active]'));
                    if(columnCollection[columnOrder]===undefined){
                         return;
                    }
                   
                    var secondLevelDescription = columnCollection[columnOrder].innerText;
                    var thirdLevelDescription = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]')? event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category"]').innerText: columnCollection[columnOrder].innerText;
                    var rowOrder = !event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category"]')? 0 : linksCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category"]')) + 1;
                    if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                        sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));
                        sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));

                    }
                    sessionStorage.setItem('topLevelMenuCoords', firstLevelDescription + '|' + secondLevelDescription + '|' + thirdLevelDescription + '|' + firstLevelPosition + '|' + columnOrder + '|' + rowOrder);

                }
            } else {
                if (event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') || ('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]')) {
                    var columnCollection = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('[class*="SubCategories-module_tab-container"] ul'));
                    var linksCollection = [].slice.apply(event.target.closest('ul').querySelectorAll('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]'));
                    var firstLevelCollection = [].slice.apply(document.querySelectorAll('[data-testid="desktop-menu-category-button"]'))

                    var firstLevelPosition = firstLevelCollection.indexOf(document.querySelector('[class*="CategoryMenuDesktop-module_active"]'))+1;
                    var firstLevelDescription = document.querySelector('[class*="CategoryMenuDesktop-module_active"] span').innerText;
                    var columnOrder = columnCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('ul'));
                    var secondLevelDescription = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') ? event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]').innerText : event.target.closest('ul').querySelector('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]').innerText;
                    var thirdLevelDescription = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') ? event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]').innerText : event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]').innerText;
                    var rowOrder = event.target.closest('[data-testid="second-level-category-link"]') ? 0 : linksCollection.indexOf(event.target.closest('[data-testid="third-level-category-link"]')) + 1;
                    if (_satellite.getVar('page_pageName') === 'home') {
                        sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));
                        sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', ui.str(firstLevelDescription, firstLevelPosition, secondLevelDescription, thirdLevelDescription, columnOrder, rowOrder));

                }

            }
        }
    });

function checkIfTesting() {
    return /hometagtest=true/i.test(document.URL);
}
if (checkIfTesting()) {
    if (document.querySelector('.site-wrapper')) {
        document.querySelector('.site-wrapper').style.background = "green";
    }

    document.body.addEventListener("click", function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
    });

}

function addHomeTagHandlers() {
    document.addEventListener('click', function(event) {
        var target = event.target;
        var elementModuleWrapper = target.closest("[data-wrapper]");
        if (elementModuleWrapper) {
            var suffix = flexibleTagging(elementModuleWrapper, target);
            if (suffix) {
                if (checkIfTesting()) {
                    alert(suffix);
                } else {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', suffix)
                    sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', suffix);
                }
            }
        }
    })
}

function flexibleTagging(parent, clickedElement) {
    var elementCTA = clickedElement.closest('[data-cta]');
    var list = elementArray('[data-cta]', parent);
    if (elementCTA && parent && list.length > 0) {
        var parentDataRef = parent.dataset.wrapper.match(/(.*)-(.*)/);
        var parentIdentifier = parentDataRef ? parentDataRef[1] : "undefined";
        var parentSectionName = parentDataRef ? parentDataRef[2] : "undefined";
        var parentPositionIndex = elementArray('[data-wrapper]').indexOf(parent) + 3;
        var containterCTA = elementCTA.closest('[data-cont]');
        var elementOrderNumber;
        var ctaOrderNumber;
        var nodeCheckImage;
        if (containterCTA) {
            elementOrderNumber = elementArray('[data-cont]', parent).length > 0 ? elementArray('[data-cont]', parent).indexOf(containterCTA) + 1 : 1;
            ctaOrderNumber = elementArray('[data-cta]', containterCTA).indexOf(elementCTA) + 1;
            nodeCheckImage = containterCTA;
        } else {
            elementOrderNumber = elementArray('[data-cta]', parent).indexOf(elementCTA) + 1;
            ctaOrderNumber = 1;
            nodeCheckImage = elementCTA;
        }

        var productCatStatic = detailSearcher(elementCTA);
        var imageSource = giveImageSrc(nodeCheckImage) ? giveImageSrc(nodeCheckImage) : giveImageSrc(parent);

        return parentIdentifier + '|' + parentPositionIndex + '|' + parentSectionName + '-' + elementOrderNumber + '|' + elementOrderNumber + '|CTA' + ctaOrderNumber + '|' + ctaOrderNumber + '|' + productCatStatic + '|' + imageSource;
    }
    return false;
}

function detailSearcher(elementCTA) {

    if(/staticPageId=.*/.test(elementCTA.href)){

        return elementCTA.href.match(/staticPageId=.*/)[0];
    }

    var detail = elementCTA.href.match(/(cat\d+|Ntt=.*|\d+)/) ? elementCTA.href.match(/(cat\d+|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1] : "undefined";
    return detail;
}

function giveImageSrc(node) {
    var nodeImageSrc = findImage(node);
    if (nodeImageSrc) {
        return nodeImageSrc;
    }
    var nodeContainer = node.closest('[data-wrapper]');
    if (nodeContainer) {
        var nodeContainerImageSrc = findImage(nodeContainer);
        if (nodeContainerImageSrc) {
            return findImage(nodeContainer);
        }
    }

    return "N/A";
}

function findImage(node2) {

    var pictureQuerySelector = node2.querySelector('source') || node2.closest('source') || node2.querySelector('img') || node2.closest('img');

    if (pictureQuerySelector && pictureQuerySelector.srcset) {
        return pictureQuerySelector.srcset.replace(/\s/gi, '').split(',')[0].replace(/\.webp\d+\w+/, ".webp").replace(/\?.*/,'');
    } else if (pictureQuerySelector && pictureQuerySelector.src) {
        return pictureQuerySelector.src.replace(/\s/gi, '').split(',')[0].replace(/\.webp\d+\w+/, ".webp").replace(/\?.*/,'');
    }
}

*/
function CyberMundosStructure(parent, clickedElement) {
    var mundo = clickedElement.closest('[class*="world__1nii4"]');
    try {
        var list = elementArray('.World_world__1nii4', mundo.closest(parent.selector));
    } catch (err) {}

    if (mundo) {
        var mundoTitle = mundo.querySelector('[class*="worldTitle__Kd3VQ"]').textContent.trim();
        var mundoOrderNumber = list.indexOf(mundo) + 1;
        var clickedPod = clickedElement.closest('[class*="podAnchor"]');
        var clickedPromoPod = clickedElement.closest('[class*="podPromoContainer"]');
        var clickedAll = clickedElement.closest('[class*="showMoreDesktopOption"]');
        var clickedAllMobile = clickedElement.closest('[class*="showmoreDropdownOption"]');
        var clickedStopper = clickedElement.closest('[class*="WorldStopper_fbStopper"]');

        if (clickedPod) {
            var podOrder = elementArray('a', mundo).indexOf(clickedPod) + 1 - elementArray('[class*="showmoreDropdownOption"]', mundo).length;
            var podDetail = clickedPod.href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1];

            var podImg = clickedPod.querySelector('img').src.match(/([^\/]+)\?|([^\/]+)\.gif|([^\/]+)\.jpg|([^\/]+)\.jpeg/)[0];
            return mundoTitle + "|" + mundoOrderNumber + "|PC" + podOrder + "|" + podOrder + "|" + podDetail + "|" + podImg;

        }
        if (clickedPromoPod) {
            var podOrder = elementArray('a', mundo).indexOf(clickedPromoPod) + 1 - elementArray('[class*="showmoreDropdownOption"]', mundo).length;
            var podDetail = clickedPromoPod.href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/) || undefined;
            if (podDetail) {
                podDetail = podDetail[1]
            }
            var podImg = clickedPromoPod.querySelector('img').src.match(/([^\/]+)\?|([^\/]+)\.gif|([^\/]+)\.jpg|([^\/]+)\.jpeg/)[0];

            return mundoTitle + "|" + mundoOrderNumber + "|PC" + podOrder + "|" + podOrder + "|" + podDetail + "|" + podImg.replace('?', '');

        }

        if (clickedAll) {
            var allText = clickedAll.querySelector("span").innerText;
            var allOrder = elementArray('[class*="showMoreDesktopOption"]', mundo).indexOf(clickedAll) + 1;
            var allDetail = clickedAll.href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1];
            return mundoTitle + "|" + mundoOrderNumber + "|Ver todo - " + allText + "|" + allOrder + "|" + allDetail + '|.';

        }

        if (clickedAllMobile) {
            var allMobileText = clickedAllMobile.querySelector("span").innerText;
            var allMobileOrder = elementArray('[class*="showmoreDropdownOption"]', mundo).indexOf(clickedAllMobile) + 1;
            var allMobileDetail = clickedAllMobile.href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1];
            return mundoTitle + "|" + mundoOrderNumber + "|Ver todo - " + allMobileText + "|" + allMobileOrder + "|" + allMobileDetail + '|.';

        }

        if (clickedStopper) {
            var stopperDetail = clickedStopper.querySelector('a').href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1];

            var stopperImg = clickedStopper.querySelector('img').src.match(/([^\/]+)\?|([^\/]+)\.gif|([^\/]+)\.jpg|([^\/]+)\.jpeg/)[0];
            return mundoTitle + "|" + mundoOrderNumber + "|Stopper " + 1 + "|" + 1 + "|" + stopperDetail + "|" + stopperImg;

        }
    }
}
function HotProduct(parent, clickedElement) {
    var hotProductItem = clickedElement.closest('[class*="carouselStyles_carouselItemInner"]');
    var hotProductContainer = clickedElement.closest('[class*="carouselStyles_carouselStrip"]');
    if (hotProductContainer && hotProductItem) {
        //var hotProductDetail = hotProductItem.querySelector('a').href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1];
        var hotProductDetail = hotProductItem.parentElement.href.match(/(cat\d+|staticPageId=.*|Ntt=.*|\d+)/)[1];
        var hotProductPos = elementArray('[class*="carouselStyles_carouselItemInner"]', hotProductContainer).indexOf(hotProductItem) + 1;
        var clickedElementImage = hotProductItem.querySelector("img").src.match(/([^\/]+)\?|([^\/]+)\.gif|([^\/]+)\.jpg|([^\/]+)\.jpeg|([^\/]+)\.svg/)[0]
        return "Lo mas Hot|1|" + hotProductDetail + "|" + hotProductPos + "|" + clickedElementImage.replace('?', '') + '|.';
    }
}
function secondLevelHandler(firstLevel, clickedElement) {
    switch (firstLevel.identifier) {
        //caselist
        //H,V, BXL, DD, PCE, M, BP, RECs, SAF,Footer
        case 'LMH':
            return HotProduct(firstLevel, clickedElement);
            break;
        case 'M':
            return CyberMundosStructure(firstLevel, clickedElement);
            break;
        default:
            break;
    }
}
function addCyberTagHandlers() {
    //S,V, BXL, DD, M, BP, RECs, SAF
    var firstLevelList = [
    {
        identifier: 'M',
        selector: '#fbra_browseHomeEventModule',
        prefix: 'M|'
    },{
        identifier: 'LMH',
        selector: '#carrusel-dy',
        prefix: 'LMH|'

    }]
    document.addEventListener('click', function (event) {

        var target = event.target;
        var validTopmostParent = firstLevelList.filter(function (firstLevel) {
            var possibleParent = firstLevel.selector && target.closest(firstLevel.selector);
            return possibleParent;
        })
        if (validTopmostParent.length > 0) {

            var elementModuleWrapper = target.closest(".fb-module-wrapper.fb-m-b");

            var suffix = secondLevelHandler(validTopmostParent[0], target);
            if (suffix) {
                if (elementModuleWrapper || suffix.match(/multicampanas/i) || suffix.match(/banners/i)) {
                    var elementPositionIndex = elementArray('.fb-module-wrapper', document.querySelector('.page-wrapper')).indexOf(elementModuleWrapper) + 8;
                    sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', (validTopmostParent[0].prefix + elementPositionIndex + '|' + suffix));
                    sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', (validTopmostParent[0].prefix + elementPositionIndex + '|' + suffix));
                } else {
                    sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', (validTopmostParent[0].prefix + suffix));
                    sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', (validTopmostParent[0].prefix + suffix));
                }
            }
        }
    })
}

//Utility functions
function elementArray(selector, parent) {
    return [].slice.apply((parent || document).querySelectorAll(selector));
}

addCyberTagHandlers();
addHomeTagHandlers();

// S|1| KEYWORD
function sendSearchString() {
    var searchText = (document.getElementById('searchForm') || document.getElementById('searchQuestionSolr') || document.getElementById('testId-SearchBar-Input')).value.trim();
    var formattedResult = 'S|1|Keyword|0|' + searchText + '|0|N/A';
    if (checkIfTesting()) {
        alert(formattedResult);
    } else {
        sessionStorage.setItem('hometag', formattedResult);
        sessionStorage.setItem('cyberString', formattedResult);
    }
}
var xy = document.getElementById('searchForm') || document.getElementById('searchQuestionSolr') || document.getElementById('testId-SearchBar-Input');
var yx = document.querySelector('.fb-masthead__util-bar__link.fb-masthead-search__box__button-search') || document.getElementById('testId-searchBar-searchIcon');
window.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
    if(e.keyCode == 13){
        if(!xy.value) return;
        sendSearchString();
    }
});

//taxonomia T|2|
function decideIfShouldTrackClick(menulink) {
    var isMenuLink = menulink.className.match(/fb-masthead__grandchild-links__item__link|fb-masthead__child-links__item__link/);
    if (isMenuLink) {
        var widthCondition = window.screen.width < 1024;
        var classCondition = menulink.className.match(/fb-masthead__child-links__item__link/);
        var finalCondition = !widthCondition || (widthCondition && !classCondition);
        return finalCondition;
    } else {
        return false;
    }
}

        if (theElement.length === 0 || theElement === null) return;
        callback();

          var thisResponse = this.response === '' || this.reponse === undefined ? this.response : JSON.parse(this.response);

        });

      };

function fixArr(arr) {
    if (typeof (arr) === "object" && arr[0] && arr[0].skuId) {
        return arr;
    }

    if (typeof (arr) === undefined) {
        return null;
    }
    var temporalArr = [];
    if (Array.isArray(arr)) {
        temporalArr = arr;
    }
    if (typeof (arr) === "string") {
        temporalArr = arr.split(",");
    }

    var fixedArray = []
    temporalArr.forEach(function(el) {
        fixedArray.push({
            "skuId": el
        });
    });
    return fixedArray;

}

function fetchProductUpdatedInfo(skuString, callback) {

    //XMLHttpRequest
    var skuObj = fixArr(skuString);
    if (skuObj) {
        var fetchItemDetailRequest = new XMLHttpRequest();
        var fetchItemDetailURL = "/s/browse/v1/fetchItemDetails/co?" + encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify({
            "products": skuObj
        }));

        fetchItemDetailRequest.addEventListener('load', function(event) {

                var response = JSON.parse(this.responseText);
                if (response.success && response.success === true) {
                    var filteredProducts = response.products.map(function(el) {
                        if (el.product.published !== false && el.product.purchasable !== false) {

                            var tempEl = {};
                            tempEl.id = el.product.id;
                            tempEl.prices = el.product.prices;
                            tempEl.prices.forEach(function(el2) {
                                el2.price = el2.originalPrice||el2.formattedLowestPrice;
                                delete el2.originalPrice;
                                delete el2.label;
                                delete el2.isLoyalty;
                                delete el2.opportunidadUnica;
                                delete el2.symbol;

                            });
                            return tempEl;

                        }
                    });
                  if(callback){
                       callback(filteredProducts);
                  }else{
                    console.log(filteredProducts);
                  }


                }

                if (response.success && response.success === false && callback) {
                     callback(null);

                }
        });

        fetchItemDetailRequest.open("GET", fetchItemDetailURL, true);
        fetchItemDetailRequest.send();
    }
}

window.fetchProductUpdatedInfo=fetchProductUpdatedInfo;
});</script><script src="//cdn.syteapi.com/assets/imajs/imajs.js?a=8344&amp;sig=5e2727779b2bac61768c4661&amp;languageCode=es_CO" async=""></script>

		syteDataLayer.push({
			name: 'fe_page_view',
			tag: 'ecommerce',
			sku: _satellite.getVar('ecom_sku')
		});
		break;
	case 'basket':

    if(digitalData.ecom.productList.length!==0){
      syteDataLayer = window.syteDataLayer || [];
		syteDataLayer.push({
			name: 'checkout_start',
			tag: 'ecommerce',
			value: getTotal(),
			currency: 'COP',
			products: getProd()
		});
  
    }
		
		break;
	default:
		syteDataLayer = window.syteDataLayer || [];
		syteDataLayer.push({
			name: 'fe_page_view',
			tag: 'ecommerce'
		});

		break;
}


function getProd() {

	var prodsArr = []
	digitalData.ecom.productList.forEach(function (el) {
		var tempObj = {
			'sku': el.sku,
			'price': el.price,
			'quantity': el.quantity
		};
		prodsArr.push(tempObj);
	});
	return prodsArr;
}

function getTotal() {
	var total = 0;
	digitalData.ecom.productList.forEach(function (el) {
		total = el.price + total;
	})
	return total;
}
